data.description: Welcome to this welcoming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in Webber-Camden! The generously sized rooms throughout the house are bathed in natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The bedrooms offer ample space, ensuring that each member of your household has their own comfortable retreat. Downstairs, the finished basement is a versatile space with a 3/4 bath. Whether you're looking for a cozy family room, a home office, or a guest suite, this lower level has you covered. Outside, the large fenced backyard beckons with room for gardening, play, and relaxation. There's also a spacious shed, providing storage for your gardening tools and outdoor equipment. This home is conveniently located near parks, including the scenic Victory Memorial Parkway, where you can enjoy leisurely walks or biking. A variety of restaurants are within easy reach, making dining out a breeze. Plus, close proximity to Downtown Mpls., I-94 and NE Mpls.
